ed="T" n="0774b08"/><persName key="A003863">釋無等</persName>姓<name>李</name>氏，今<placeName key="PL000000023389"><placeName>東京</placeName><placeName>尉氏</placeName></placeName>人也。負志卓犖，<lb
ed="T" n="0774b09"/>辭氣貞正。少隨父官于<placeName key="PL000000019349">南康</placeName>，頻遊<name>梵</name>剎，向<lb
ed="T" n="0774b10"/>僧瞻像，往即忘歸。既作沙門，遇<persName key="A003623">道一<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName><lb
ed="T" n="0774b11"/>在<placeName key="PL000000019334">龔公山</placeName>，學侶螘慕<ptr type="glossary" target="#g931"/>。<persName key="A003863">等</persName>求法於其間，挺然<lb
ed="T" n="0774b12"/>出類。<date from-iso="+0812-02-21" key="j20176882018041" to-iso="+0813-02-08"><name>元和</name>七年</date>遊<placeName key="PL000000027119">漢上</placeName><ptr target="#n1478"/>。後至<placeName key="PL000000027409">武昌</placeName>，覩郡西<lb
ed="T" n="0774b13"/><placeName key="PL000000026442">黃鵠山</placeName>奇秀，遂結茅分衛。由此<placeName key="PL000000037154">巴</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000035107">蜀</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000027770">荊</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000027118">襄</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0774b14"/>尚玄理者，無遠不至矣。<date from-iso="+0827-03-18" key="j20231922023504" to-iso="+0828-01-24"><name>大和</name>元載</date>，屬相國<lb
ed="T" n="0774b15"/><persName key="A010440">牛<roleName>公</roleName>僧孺</persName>出鎮<ref type="place" target="#PL000000026483">三江</ref><ptr target="#n1548"/>，聞<persName key="A003863">等</persName>道香，普熏遐邇，<lb
ed="T" n="0774b16"/>命駕枉問。風虎相須<ptr target="#n2649"/>，為法重人。<persName key="A010440">牛<roleName>公</roleName></persName>慮其<lb
ed="T" n="0774b17"/>蘭若不隸名<anchor xml:id="beg0774sgsz15"/>籍<anchor xml:id="end0774sgsz15"/>，特為<anchor xml:id="beg0774sgsz16"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>秦</sic><corr>奏</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0774sgsz16"/>題曰「大寂」也。憧憧<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1486"/><lb
ed="T" n="0774b18"/>往來，堂無虛<anchor xml:id="beg0774sgsz17"/>位<anchor xml:id="end0774sgsz17"/>。至<date from-iso="+0830-10-25" key="j20245092024537" to-iso="+0830-11-22">四年十月</date>示滅，年八十<lb
ed="T" n="0774b19"/>二。弟子<persName key="A019211">誓通</persName>奉全身入塔焉。</p>
